headline: Will Trump’s 200% tariff threat on pharma really materialize?
summary: Investing.com -- Trump’s threat to slap a 200% tariff on pharmaceutical imports, made offhandedly at a cabinet meeting, has sparked a selloff in some drug stocks, but analysts say the number may be more political posturing than economic policy.
